        "data": {
          "title": "Sudden Accident",
          "content": "The cause of your death was outside forces which you had no control over.\n\nYou were in the wrong place at the wrong time.\n\nPerhaps you were a pedestrian in a crosswalk who was ran over by a drunk driver.\n\nOr a victim killed in a terrorist attack.\n\nPerhaps a powerful earthquake left your broken body buried in the rubble that you once called your home.\n\nOn the bright side of things, you were completely blindsided by \n\nDeath so you didn't have to ruminate on your approaching demise.\n\nOn the bleaker side, there is nothing you could have done to avoid this ending to your life...which feels as helpless as it sounds.\n\nLooking back at your place and time of death, how important would you say it was that you were there at that particular time?",
          "blockType": "narrative",
          "choices": [
            {
              "label": "Not at all important",
              "choiceKind": "goTo",
              "playerMessage": "",
              "npcResponse": "",
              "targetNodeId": "node_hxzt8696",
